  "segments": [
    {
      "id": "c01-p01-u01",
      "sceneId": "c01-p01",
      "chapterIndex": 0,
      "paragraphIndex": 0,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "你知道 AI 智能体为什么会自信猜错，还直接替你行动吗？",
      "gapBefore": 0,
      "audioDuration": 5.52,
      "audioStart": 0,
      "spokenStart": 0.191,
      "spokenEnd": 4.715,
      "actualGapBefore": 0
    },
    {
      "id": "c01-p02-u01",
      "sceneId": "c01-p02",
      "chapterIndex": 0,
      "paragraphIndex": 1,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "OpenAI 的研究给出一个关键原因：常见的准确率评分，可能让猜测比诚实说不知道更容易得分。",
      "gapBefore": 0.5,
      "audioDuration": 8.568,
      "audioStart": 5.017,
      "spokenStart": 5.215,
      "spokenEnd": 12.795,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.5
    },
    {
      "id": "c01-p03-u01",
      "sceneId": "c01-p03",
      "chapterIndex": 0,
      "paragraphIndex": 2,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "后果不只是答错一道题。",
      "gapBefore": 0.5,
      "audioDuration": 2.736,
      "audioStart": 13.102,
      "spokenStart": 13.295,
      "spokenEnd": 15.063,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.5
    },
    {
      "id": "c01-p03-u02",
      "sceneId": "c01-p03",
      "chapterIndex": 0,
      "paragraphIndex": 2,
      "utteranceIndex": 1,
      "text": "比如智能体拿着一份旧物流记录，断言订单四八二周五送达，还准备自动回复客户，甚至触发退款。",
      "gapBefore": 0.25,
      "audioDuration": 8.808,
      "audioStart": 15.135,
      "spokenStart": 15.313,
      "spokenEnd": 23.152,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.25
    },
    {
      "id": "c01-p04-u01",
      "sceneId": "c01-p04",
      "chapterIndex": 0,
      "paragraphIndex": 3,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "这期会做一张可执行的 AI 智能体事实核验清单。",
      "gapBefore": 0.5,
      "audioDuration": 5.28,
      "audioStart": 23.465,
      "spokenStart": 23.652,
      "spokenEnd": 27.965,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.5
    },
    {
      "id": "c01-p04-u02",
      "sceneId": "c01-p04",
      "chapterIndex": 0,
      "paragraphIndex": 3,
      "utteranceIndex": 1,
      "text": "它帮你决定什么时候回答、什么时候查证、什么时候澄清，以及什么时候必须停止。",
      "gapBefore": 0.25,
      "audioDuration": 7.32,
      "audioStart": 28.027,
      "spokenStart": 28.215,
      "spokenEnd": 34.565,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.25
    },
    {
      "id": "c01-p05-u01",
      "sceneId": "c01-p05",
      "chapterIndex": 0,
      "paragraphIndex": 4,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "我会用订单四八二这个案例贯穿全片，只回答三个问题：它为什么会猜，它到底知不知道，以及怎样核验后再行动。",
      "gapBefore": 0.5,
      "audioDuration": 9.768,
      "audioStart": 34.871,
      "spokenStart": 35.065,
      "spokenEnd": 43.855,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.5
    },
    {
      "id": "c01-p06-u01",
      "sceneId": "c01-p06",
      "chapterIndex": 0,
      "paragraphIndex": 5,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "视频全程干货高价值，让你成为更擅长使用 AI 的人，内容较长，点点关注收藏不迷路。",
      "gapBefore": 0.5,
      "audioDuration": 8.064,
      "audioStart": 44.173,
      "spokenStart": 44.355,
      "spokenEnd": 51.441,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.5
    },
    {
      "id": "c02-p01-u01",
      "sceneId": "c02-p01",
      "chapterIndex": 1,
      "paragraphIndex": 0,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "先看机制：AI 智能体为什么会猜。",
      "gapBefore": 0.8,
      "audioDuration": 3.696,
      "audioStart": 52.057,
      "spokenStart": 52.241,
      "spokenEnd": 54.972,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.8
    },
    {
      "id": "c02-p01-u02",
      "sceneId": "c02-p01",
      "chapterIndex": 1,
      "paragraphIndex": 0,
      "utteranceIndex": 1,
      "text": "这一章不堆概念，只建立一个判断——说得流畅，和事实已经成立，是两件不同的事。",
      "gapBefore": 0.25,
      "audioDuration": 7.584,
      "audioStart": 55.034,
      "spokenStart": 55.222,
      "spokenEnd": 61.85,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.25
    },
    {
      "id": "c02-p02-u01",
      "sceneId": "c02-p02",
      "chapterIndex": 1,
      "paragraphIndex": 1,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "回到订单四八二。",
      "gapBefore": 0.5,
      "audioDuration": 2.088,
      "audioStart": 62.166,
      "spokenStart": 62.35,
      "spokenEnd": 63.469,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.5
    },
    {
      "id": "c02-p02-u02",
      "sceneId": "c02-p02",
      "chapterIndex": 1,
      "paragraphIndex": 1,
      "utteranceIndex": 1,
      "text": "智能体在旧页面里看到“预计周五送达”，语言和格式都很完整，于是把一条历史预测，当成了今天仍然有效的事实。",
      "gapBefore": 0.25,
      "audioDuration": 9.744,
      "audioStart": 63.524,
      "spokenStart": 63.719,
      "spokenEnd": 72.483,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.25
    },
    {
      "id": "c02-p03-u01",
      "sceneId": "c02-p03",
      "chapterIndex": 1,
      "paragraphIndex": 2,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "模型在预训练中学习的是文字怎样接在一起，不会为每句话自动附上一张可靠的真假标签。",
      "gapBefore": 0.5,
      "audioDuration": 8.592,
      "audioStart": 72.79,
      "spokenStart": 72.983,
      "spokenEnd": 80.586,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.5
    },
    {
      "id": "c02-p03-u02",
      "sceneId": "c02-p03",
      "chapterIndex": 1,
      "paragraphIndex": 2,
      "utteranceIndex": 1,
      "text": "高频而稳定的事实比较容易学到；",
      "gapBefore": 0.25,
      "audioDuration": 3.48,
      "audioStart": 80.649,
      "spokenStart": 80.836,
      "spokenEnd": 83.321,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.25
    },
    {
      "id": "c02-p03-u03",
      "sceneId": "c02-p03",
      "chapterIndex": 1,
      "paragraphIndex": 2,
      "utteranceIndex": 2,
      "text": "冷门生日、内部文件名或某一笔订单状态这类任意低频事实，缺少规律时就很难从语言模式补回真相。",
      "gapBefore": 0.25,
      "audioDuration": 9.888,
      "audioStart": 83.384,
      "spokenStart": 83.571,
      "spokenEnd": 92.48,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.25
    },
    {
      "id": "c02-p04-u01",
      "sceneId": "c02-p04",
      "chapterIndex": 1,
      "paragraphIndex": 3,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "后训练本来应该减少错误，但如果评测只看准确率，猜测仍可能赢。",
      "gapBefore": 0.5,
      "audioDuration": 6.48,
      "audioStart": 92.792,
      "spokenStart": 92.98,
      "spokenEnd": 98.473,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.5
    },
    {
      "id": "c02-p04-u02",
      "sceneId": "c02-p04",
      "chapterIndex": 1,
      "paragraphIndex": 3,
      "utteranceIndex": 1,
      "text": "猜一个生日有三百六十五分之一的命中机会；",
      "gapBefore": 0.25,
      "audioDuration": 4.2,
      "audioStart": 98.552,
      "spokenStart": 98.723,
      "spokenEnd": 101.971,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.25
    },
    {
      "id": "c02-p04-u03",
      "sceneId": "c02-p04",
      "chapterIndex": 1,
      "paragraphIndex": 3,
      "utteranceIndex": 2,
      "text": "说不知道虽然避免了自信错误，却保证拿不到命中分。",
      "gapBefore": 0.25,
      "audioDuration": 5.208,
      "audioStart": 102.04,
      "spokenStart": 102.221,
      "spokenEnd": 106.459,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.25
    },
    {
      "id": "c02-p05-u01",
      "sceneId": "c02-p05",
      "chapterIndex": 1,
      "paragraphIndex": 4,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "OpenAI 在 SimpleQA 中给过一个很直观的对比。",
      "gapBefore": 0.5,
      "audioDuration": 4.368,
      "audioStart": 106.764,
      "spokenStart": 106.959,
      "spokenEnd": 110.341,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.5
    },
    {
      "id": "c02-p05-u02",
      "sceneId": "c02-p05",
      "chapterIndex": 1,
      "paragraphIndex": 4,
      "utteranceIndex": 1,
      "text": "一个模型准确率百分之二十二、错误率百分之二十六、拒答率百分之五十二；",
      "gapBefore": 0.25,
      "audioDuration": 6.624,
      "audioStart": 110.402,
      "spokenStart": 110.591,
      "spokenEnd": 116.238,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.25
    },
    {
      "id": "c02-p05-u03",
      "sceneId": "c02-p05",
      "chapterIndex": 1,
      "paragraphIndex": 4,
      "utteranceIndex": 2,
      "text": "另一个模型准确率只高两点，错误率却升到百分之七十五，而且几乎不拒答。",
      "gapBefore": 0.25,
      "audioDuration": 7.056,
      "audioStart": 116.302,
      "spokenStart": 116.488,
      "spokenEnd": 122.589,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.25
    },
    {
      "id": "c02-p06-u01",
      "sceneId": "c02-p06",
      "chapterIndex": 1,
      "paragraphIndex": 5,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "这说明相近的准确率，可以藏着完全不同的可靠性。",
      "gapBefore": 0.5,
      "audioDuration": 4.896,
      "audioStart": 122.898,
      "spokenStart": 123.089,
      "spokenEnd": 126.995,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.5
    },
    {
      "id": "c02-p06-u02",
      "sceneId": "c02-p06",
      "chapterIndex": 1,
      "paragraphIndex": 5,
      "utteranceIndex": 1,
      "text": "好的评分不能只奖励答对，还要让自信错误付出更高代价，并奖励有根据的澄清、核验和拒答。",
      "gapBefore": 0.25,
      "audioDuration": 9,
      "audioStart": 127.057,
      "spokenStart": 127.245,
      "spokenEnd": 135.29,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.25
    },
    {
      "id": "c02-p07-u01",
      "sceneId": "c02-p07",
      "chapterIndex": 1,
      "paragraphIndex": 6,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "所以订单案例里的“周五送达”不是凭空胡说，它来自一条看起来合理的旧记录。",
      "gapBefore": 0.5,
      "audioDuration": 6.72,
      "audioStart": 135.619,
      "spokenStart": 135.79,
      "spokenEnd": 141.547,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.5
    },
    {
      "id": "c02-p07-u02",
      "sceneId": "c02-p07",
      "chapterIndex": 1,
      "paragraphIndex": 6,
      "utteranceIndex": 1,
      "text": "真正的错误，是系统把“有可能”直接升级成“已确认”，又允许这句话进入执行链。",
      "gapBefore": 0.25,
      "audioDuration": 7.152,
      "audioStart": 141.605,
      "spokenStart": 141.797,
      "spokenEnd": 147.97,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.25
    },
    {
      "id": "c02-p08-u01",
      "sceneId": "c02-p08",
      "chapterIndex": 1,
      "paragraphIndex": 7,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "本章小节：流畅只说明表达连贯，不说明事实已核验；",
      "gapBefore": 0.5,
      "audioDuration": 5.376,
      "audioStart": 148.286,
      "spokenStart": 148.47,
      "spokenEnd": 152.878,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.5
    },
    {
      "id": "c02-p08-u02",
      "sceneId": "c02-p08",
      "chapterIndex": 1,
      "paragraphIndex": 7,
      "utteranceIndex": 1,
      "text": "只看准确率会奖励幸运猜测；",
      "gapBefore": 0.25,
      "audioDuration": 3.336,
      "audioStart": 152.944,
      "spokenStart": 153.128,
      "spokenEnd": 155.485,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.25
    },
    {
      "id": "c02-p08-u03",
      "sceneId": "c02-p08",
      "chapterIndex": 1,
      "paragraphIndex": 7,
      "utteranceIndex": 2,
      "text": "真正可靠的系统，要让错误代价和诚实边界一起进入评分。",
      "gapBefore": 0.25,
      "audioDuration": 6.024,
      "audioStart": 155.542,
      "spokenStart": 155.735,
      "spokenEnd": 160.789,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.25
    },
    {
      "id": "c03-p01-u01",
      "sceneId": "c03-p01",
      "chapterIndex": 2,
      "paragraphIndex": 0,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "第二步，判断 AI 智能体到底知不知道。",
      "gapBefore": 0.8,
      "audioDuration": 4.392,
      "audioStart": 161.394,
      "spokenStart": 161.589,
      "spokenEnd": 165.002,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.8
    },
    {
      "id": "c03-p01-u02",
      "sceneId": "c03-p01",
      "chapterIndex": 2,
      "paragraphIndex": 0,
      "utteranceIndex": 1,
      "text": "这里要建立一扇可答性门：先判断现有信息能否支持答案，再评价答案听起来像不像真的。",
      "gapBefore": 0.25,
      "audioDuration": 8.328,
      "audioStart": 165.074,
      "spokenStart": 165.252,
      "spokenEnd": 172.611,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.25
    },
    {
      "id": "c03-p02-u01",
      "sceneId": "c03-p02",
      "chapterIndex": 2,
      "paragraphIndex": 1,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "可答性先查四件事：问题是否具体，所需信息是否可得，事实是否新到不能依赖记忆，以及结果能否在行动前验证。",
      "gapBefore": 0.5,
      "audioDuration": 10.872,
      "audioStart": 172.925,
      "spokenStart": 173.111,
      "spokenEnd": 183.001,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.5
    },
    {
      "id": "c03-p02-u02",
      "sceneId": "c03-p02",
      "chapterIndex": 2,
      "paragraphIndex": 1,
      "utteranceIndex": 1,
      "text": "订单四八二现在就缺少查询日期、实时物流扫描和系统访问权限。",
      "gapBefore": 0.25,
      "audioDuration": 6.6,
      "audioStart": 183.066,
      "spokenStart": 183.251,
      "spokenEnd": 188.888,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.25
    },
    {
      "id": "c03-p03-u01",
      "sceneId": "c03-p03",
      "chapterIndex": 2,
      "paragraphIndex": 2,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "如果日期、对象、时间范围或术语不清，先澄清。",
      "gapBefore": 0.5,
      "audioDuration": 5.448,
      "audioStart": 189.203,
      "spokenStart": 189.388,
      "spokenEnd": 193.882,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.5
    },
    {
      "id": "c03-p03-u02",
      "sceneId": "c03-p03",
      "chapterIndex": 2,
      "paragraphIndex": 2,
      "utteranceIndex": 1,
      "text": "不要问一串泛泛的问题，只追问真正会改变结论的最小信息，例如：你问的是今天的预计送达时间，还是下单时的承诺时间？",
      "gapBefore": 0.25,
      "audioDuration": 10.536,
      "audioStart": 193.945,
      "spokenStart": 194.132,
      "spokenEnd": 203.685,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.25
    },
    {
      "id": "c03-p04-u01",
      "sceneId": "c03-p04",
      "chapterIndex": 2,
      "paragraphIndex": 3,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "价格、法规、日程、账户状态、库存和私有订单，只能靠实时或已授权的证据回答。",
      "gapBefore": 0.5,
      "audioDuration": 8.328,
      "audioStart": 204.01,
      "spokenStart": 204.185,
      "spokenEnd": 211.565,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.5
    },
    {
      "id": "c03-p04-u02",
      "sceneId": "c03-p04",
      "chapterIndex": 2,
      "paragraphIndex": 3,
      "utteranceIndex": 1,
      "text": "智能体没有物流接口权限时，不是“置信度较低”，而是缺少知道当前状态的能力。",
      "gapBefore": 0.25,
      "audioDuration": 7.152,
      "audioStart": 211.619,
      "spokenStart": 211.815,
      "spokenEnd": 217.98,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.25
    },
    {
      "id": "c03-p05-u01",
      "sceneId": "c03-p05",
      "chapterIndex": 2,
      "paragraphIndex": 4,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "有些问题即使信息很多，也没有唯一答案。",
      "gapBefore": 0.5,
      "audioDuration": 4.344,
      "audioStart": 218.297,
      "spokenStart": 218.48,
      "spokenEnd": 221.837,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.5
    },
    {
      "id": "c03-p05-u02",
      "sceneId": "c03-p05",
      "chapterIndex": 2,
      "paragraphIndex": 4,
      "utteranceIndex": 1,
      "text": "多个解释都符合描述时，智能体应该说明歧义，给出最小有用选择，而不是把其中一个猜成用户的隐藏意图。",
      "gapBefore": 0.25,
      "audioDuration": 9.912,
      "audioStart": 221.893,
      "spokenStart": 222.087,
      "spokenEnd": 231.024,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.25
    },
    {
      "id": "c03-p06-u01",
      "sceneId": "c03-p06",
      "chapterIndex": 2,
      "paragraphIndex": 5,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "证据门槛还要跟后果一起变化。",
      "gapBefore": 0.5,
      "audioDuration": 3.48,
      "audioStart": 231.339,
      "spokenStart": 231.524,
      "spokenEnd": 234.015,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.5
    },
    {
      "id": "c03-p06-u02",
      "sceneId": "c03-p06",
      "chapterIndex": 2,
      "paragraphIndex": 5,
      "utteranceIndex": 1,
      "text": "写几个创意标题可以容许近似；",
      "gapBefore": 0.25,
      "audioDuration": 3.384,
      "audioStart": 234.082,
      "spokenStart": 234.265,
      "spokenEnd": 236.677,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.25
    },
    {
      "id": "c03-p06-u03",
      "sceneId": "c03-p06",
      "chapterIndex": 2,
      "paragraphIndex": 5,
      "utteranceIndex": 2,
      "text": "涉及金钱、健康、权限、公开发布或客户承诺时，同样的“不确定”必须触发更严格的核验。",
      "gapBefore": 0.25,
      "audioDuration": 8.904,
      "audioStart": 236.743,
      "spokenStart": 236.927,
      "spokenEnd": 244.862,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.25
    },
    {
      "id": "c03-p07-u01",
      "sceneId": "c03-p07",
      "chapterIndex": 2,
      "paragraphIndex": 6,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "通过可答性门之后，把关键判断标成四种状态：已确认、有支持但不完整、推断、未知。",
      "gapBefore": 0.5,
      "audioDuration": 9.048,
      "audioStart": 245.183,
      "spokenStart": 245.362,
      "spokenEnd": 253.44,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.5
    },
    {
      "id": "c03-p07-u02",
      "sceneId": "c03-p07",
      "chapterIndex": 2,
      "paragraphIndex": 6,
      "utteranceIndex": 1,
      "text": "这样“订单存在”可以是已确认，“周五送达”只是推断，“最新仓库扫描”则仍然未知。",
      "gapBefore": 0.25,
      "audioDuration": 7.32,
      "audioStart": 253.504,
      "spokenStart": 253.69,
      "spokenEnd": 260.038,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.25
    },
    {
      "id": "c03-p08-u01",
      "sceneId": "c03-p08",
      "chapterIndex": 2,
      "paragraphIndex": 7,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "置信度必须跟随证据覆盖，而不是跟随措辞流畅。",
      "gapBefore": 0.5,
      "audioDuration": 4.944,
      "audioStart": 260.347,
      "spokenStart": 260.538,
      "spokenEnd": 264.502,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.5
    },
    {
      "id": "c03-p08-u02",
      "sceneId": "c03-p08",
      "chapterIndex": 2,
      "paragraphIndex": 7,
      "utteranceIndex": 1,
      "text": "除非系统真的针对这类任务做过校准，否则不要写“百分之八十七可信”这种漂亮但无来源的数字。",
      "gapBefore": 0.25,
      "audioDuration": 8.232,
      "audioStart": 264.563,
      "spokenStart": 264.752,
      "spokenEnd": 272.011,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.25
    },
    {
      "id": "c03-p09-u01",
      "sceneId": "c03-p09",
      "chapterIndex": 2,
      "paragraphIndex": 8,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "每个重要判断都要连到它自己的证据。",
      "gapBefore": 0.5,
      "audioDuration": 3.768,
      "audioStart": 272.318,
      "spokenStart": 272.511,
      "spokenEnd": 275.307,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.5
    },
    {
      "id": "c03-p09-u02",
      "sceneId": "c03-p09",
      "chapterIndex": 2,
      "paragraphIndex": 8,
      "utteranceIndex": 1,
      "text": "证据只证明订单已经发货，就只能写“已发货”；",
      "gapBefore": 0.25,
      "audioDuration": 4.848,
      "audioStart": 275.37,
      "spokenStart": 275.557,
      "spokenEnd": 279.429,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.25
    },
    {
      "id": "c03-p09-u03",
      "sceneId": "c03-p09",
      "chapterIndex": 2,
      "paragraphIndex": 8,
      "utteranceIndex": 2,
      "text": "不能顺手扩成“周五必达”，更不能把一条长引用当作所有结论的通行证。",
      "gapBefore": 0.25,
      "audioDuration": 6.696,
      "audioStart": 279.492,
      "spokenStart": 279.679,
      "spokenEnd": 285.388,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.25
    },
    {
      "id": "c03-p10-u01",
      "sceneId": "c03-p10",
      "chapterIndex": 2,
      "paragraphIndex": 9,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "再把未知连接到动作。",
      "gapBefore": 0.5,
      "audioDuration": 2.52,
      "audioStart": 285.713,
      "spokenStart": 285.888,
      "spokenEnd": 287.442,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.5
    },
    {
      "id": "c03-p10-u02",
      "sceneId": "c03-p10",
      "chapterIndex": 2,
      "paragraphIndex": 9,
      "utteranceIndex": 1,
      "text": "订单存在，可以继续；",
      "gapBefore": 0.25,
      "audioDuration": 2.712,
      "audioStart": 287.511,
      "spokenStart": 287.692,
      "spokenEnd": 289.429,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.25
    },
    {
      "id": "c03-p10-u03",
      "sceneId": "c03-p10",
      "chapterIndex": 2,
      "paragraphIndex": 9,
      "utteranceIndex": 2,
      "text": "周五送达，需要查实时物流；",
      "gapBefore": 0.25,
      "audioDuration": 3.216,
      "audioStart": 289.495,
      "spokenStart": 289.679,
      "spokenEnd": 291.925,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.25
    },
    {
      "id": "c03-p10-u04",
      "sceneId": "c03-p10",
      "chapterIndex": 2,
      "paragraphIndex": 9,
      "utteranceIndex": 3,
      "text": "扫描缺失，要请求权限或向客户说明暂时无法确认；",
      "gapBefore": 0.25,
      "audioDuration": 5.76,
      "audioStart": 291.989,
      "spokenStart": 292.175,
      "spokenEnd": 296.963,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.25
    },
    {
      "id": "c03-p10-u05",
      "sceneId": "c03-p10",
      "chapterIndex": 2,
      "paragraphIndex": 9,
      "utteranceIndex": 4,
      "text": "在证据回来前，自动回复和退款都先暂停。",
      "gapBefore": 0.25,
      "audioDuration": 4.584,
      "audioStart": 297.041,
      "spokenStart": 297.213,
      "spokenEnd": 300.856,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.25
    },
    {
      "id": "c03-p11-u01",
      "sceneId": "c03-p11",
      "chapterIndex": 2,
      "paragraphIndex": 10,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "本章小节：先过可答性门，再把判断分成已确认、推断和未知；",
      "gapBefore": 0.5,
      "audioDuration": 6.432,
      "audioStart": 301.17,
      "spokenStart": 301.356,
      "spokenEnd": 306.818,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.5
    },
    {
      "id": "c03-p11-u02",
      "sceneId": "c03-p11",
      "chapterIndex": 2,
      "paragraphIndex": 10,
      "utteranceIndex": 1,
      "text": "置信度只跟随证据；",
      "gapBefore": 0.25,
      "audioDuration": 2.448,
      "audioStart": 306.882,
      "spokenStart": 307.068,
      "spokenEnd": 308.549,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.25
    },
    {
      "id": "c03-p11-u03",
      "sceneId": "c03-p11",
      "chapterIndex": 2,
      "paragraphIndex": 10,
      "utteranceIndex": 2,
      "text": "每个未知都必须落到澄清、核验、申请权限或停止中的一个动作。",
      "gapBefore": 0.25,
      "audioDuration": 6.648,
      "audioStart": 308.611,
      "spokenStart": 308.799,
      "spokenEnd": 314.479,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.25
    },
    {
      "id": "c04-p01-u01",
      "sceneId": "c04-p01",
      "chapterIndex": 3,
      "paragraphIndex": 0,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "第三步，把不确定性接到行动。",
      "gapBefore": 0.8,
      "audioDuration": 3.264,
      "audioStart": 315.094,
      "spokenStart": 315.279,
      "spokenEnd": 317.573,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.8
    },
    {
      "id": "c04-p01-u02",
      "sceneId": "c04-p01",
      "chapterIndex": 3,
      "paragraphIndex": 0,
      "utteranceIndex": 1,
      "text": "这一章会把刚才的判断变成一张六步清单，并让订单四八二真正走完一次核验。",
      "gapBefore": 0.25,
      "audioDuration": 7.368,
      "audioStart": 317.638,
      "spokenStart": 317.823,
      "spokenEnd": 324.232,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.25
    },
    {
      "id": "c04-p02-u01",
      "sceneId": "c04-p02",
      "chapterIndex": 3,
      "paragraphIndex": 1,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "先按后果分配精力。",
      "gapBefore": 0.5,
      "audioDuration": 2.472,
      "audioStart": 324.548,
      "spokenStart": 324.732,
      "spokenEnd": 326.232,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.5
    },
    {
      "id": "c04-p02-u02",
      "sceneId": "c04-p02",
      "chapterIndex": 3,
      "paragraphIndex": 1,
      "utteranceIndex": 1,
      "text": "给客户发送一条可更正的进度说明，风险相对较低；",
      "gapBefore": 0.25,
      "audioDuration": 5.04,
      "audioStart": 326.294,
      "spokenStart": 326.482,
      "spokenEnd": 330.563,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.25
    },
    {
      "id": "c04-p02-u03",
      "sceneId": "c04-p02",
      "chapterIndex": 3,
      "paragraphIndex": 1,
      "utteranceIndex": 2,
      "text": "承诺具体日期或自动退款，会影响信任和金钱，必须使用更高证据门槛。",
      "gapBefore": 0.25,
      "audioDuration": 7.176,
      "audioStart": 330.624,
      "spokenStart": 330.813,
      "spokenEnd": 337.011,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.25
    },
    {
      "id": "c04-p03-u01",
      "sceneId": "c04-p03",
      "chapterIndex": 3,
      "paragraphIndex": 2,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "一手证据要尽量靠近事实本身。",
      "gapBefore": 0.5,
      "audioDuration": 3.576,
      "audioStart": 337.323,
      "spokenStart": 337.511,
      "spokenEnd": 340.114,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.5
    },
    {
      "id": "c04-p03-u02",
      "sceneId": "c04-p03",
      "chapterIndex": 3,
      "paragraphIndex": 2,
      "utteranceIndex": 1,
      "text": "订单状态查订单数据库，物流进度查承运商接口，规则查当前官方政策，研究结论查原论文，任务完成则检查真实产物，而不是只看智能体的总结。",
      "gapBefore": 0.25,
      "audioDuration": 13.248,
      "audioStart": 340.178,
      "spokenStart": 340.364,
      "spokenEnd": 352.657,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.25
    },
    {
      "id": "c04-p04-u01",
      "sceneId": "c04-p04",
      "chapterIndex": 3,
      "paragraphIndex": 3,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "单一来源可能过期、偏颇、不完整或被误读时，再找真正独立的证据。",
      "gapBefore": 0.5,
      "audioDuration": 6.912,
      "audioStart": 352.97,
      "spokenStart": 353.157,
      "spokenEnd": 359.103,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.5
    },
    {
      "id": "c04-p04-u02",
      "sceneId": "c04-p04",
      "chapterIndex": 3,
      "paragraphIndex": 3,
      "utteranceIndex": 1,
      "text": "两个网页都复制同一句没有出处的话，不是两份证明；",
      "gapBefore": 0.25,
      "audioDuration": 4.944,
      "audioStart": 359.16,
      "spokenStart": 359.353,
      "spokenEnd": 363.308,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.25
    },
    {
      "id": "c04-p04-u03",
      "sceneId": "c04-p04",
      "chapterIndex": 3,
      "paragraphIndex": 3,
      "utteranceIndex": 2,
      "text": "订单系统和承运商的最新扫描，才是两个不同的观察点。",
      "gapBefore": 0.25,
      "audioDuration": 5.064,
      "audioStart": 363.374,
      "spokenStart": 363.558,
      "spokenEnd": 367.642,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.25
    },
    {
      "id": "c04-p05-u01",
      "sceneId": "c04-p05",
      "chapterIndex": 3,
      "paragraphIndex": 4,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "证据还必须对应准确判断。",
      "gapBefore": 0.5,
      "audioDuration": 2.976,
      "audioStart": 367.946,
      "spokenStart": 368.142,
      "spokenEnd": 370.126,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.5
    },
    {
      "id": "c04-p05-u02",
      "sceneId": "c04-p05",
      "chapterIndex": 3,
      "paragraphIndex": 4,
      "utteranceIndex": 1,
      "text": "证明产品存在，不等于证明某个功能可用；",
      "gapBefore": 0.25,
      "audioDuration": 4.08,
      "audioStart": 370.191,
      "spokenStart": 370.376,
      "spokenEnd": 373.476,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.25
    },
    {
      "id": "c04-p05-u03",
      "sceneId": "c04-p05",
      "chapterIndex": 3,
      "paragraphIndex": 4,
      "utteranceIndex": 2,
      "text": "一项受控实验有效，也不等于所有场景都有效；",
      "gapBefore": 0.25,
      "audioDuration": 4.608,
      "audioStart": 373.544,
      "spokenStart": 373.726,
      "spokenEnd": 377.363,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.25
    },
    {
      "id": "c04-p05-u04",
      "sceneId": "c04-p05",
      "chapterIndex": 3,
      "paragraphIndex": 4,
      "utteranceIndex": 3,
      "text": "看到包裹离开仓库，也不等于能承诺周五送达。",
      "gapBefore": 0.25,
      "audioDuration": 4.752,
      "audioStart": 377.426,
      "spokenStart": 377.613,
      "spokenEnd": 381.393,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.25
    },
    {
      "id": "c04-p06-u01",
      "sceneId": "c04-p06",
      "chapterIndex": 3,
      "paragraphIndex": 5,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "接着核对日期、范围、对象、单位和例外。",
      "gapBefore": 0.5,
      "audioDuration": 4.464,
      "audioStart": 381.718,
      "spokenStart": 381.893,
      "spokenEnd": 385.398,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.5
    },
    {
      "id": "c04-p06-u02",
      "sceneId": "c04-p06",
      "chapterIndex": 3,
      "paragraphIndex": 5,
      "utteranceIndex": 1,
      "text": "许多自信错误引用了真实信息，只是把它贴到了错误时间、错误订单、错误地区，或忽略了节假日这个例外。",
      "gapBefore": 0.25,
      "audioDuration": 9.48,
      "audioStart": 385.47,
      "spokenStart": 385.648,
      "spokenEnd": 394.174,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.25
    },
    {
      "id": "c04-p07-u01",
      "sceneId": "c04-p07",
      "chapterIndex": 3,
      "paragraphIndex": 6,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "最后看行动是否可逆。",
      "gapBefore": 0.5,
      "audioDuration": 2.808,
      "audioStart": 394.501,
      "spokenStart": 394.674,
      "spokenEnd": 396.52,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.5
    },
    {
      "id": "c04-p07-u02",
      "sceneId": "c04-p07",
      "chapterIndex": 3,
      "paragraphIndex": 6,
      "utteranceIndex": 1,
      "text": "智能体可以收集证据、起草回复和提出建议；",
      "gapBefore": 0.25,
      "audioDuration": 4.608,
      "audioStart": 396.586,
      "spokenStart": 396.77,
      "spokenEnd": 400.4,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.25
    },
    {
      "id": "c04-p07-u03",
      "sceneId": "c04-p07",
      "chapterIndex": 3,
      "paragraphIndex": 6,
      "utteranceIndex": 2,
      "text": "但退款、改权限、公开发布或其他高影响操作，在执行前仍要保留明确的人工批准。",
      "gapBefore": 0.25,
      "audioDuration": 8.352,
      "audioStart": 400.465,
      "spokenStart": 400.65,
      "spokenEnd": 408.014,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.25
    },
    {
      "id": "c04-p08-u01",
      "sceneId": "c04-p08",
      "chapterIndex": 3,
      "paragraphIndex": 7,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "现在看六步清单。",
      "gapBefore": 0.5,
      "audioDuration": 2.328,
      "audioStart": 408.331,
      "spokenStart": 408.514,
      "spokenEnd": 409.872,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.5
    },
    {
      "id": "c04-p08-u02",
      "sceneId": "c04-p08",
      "chapterIndex": 3,
      "paragraphIndex": 7,
      "utteranceIndex": 1,
      "text": "第一步是可答性：写清问题、对象、时间范围、时效要求、可用工具，以及阻塞可靠回答的缺失信息。",
      "gapBefore": 0.25,
      "audioDuration": 9.744,
      "audioStart": 409.937,
      "spokenStart": 410.122,
      "spokenEnd": 418.918,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.25
    },
    {
      "id": "c04-p09-u01",
      "sceneId": "c04-p09",
      "chapterIndex": 3,
      "paragraphIndex": 8,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "第二步列关键判断，把它们标成已确认、推断或未知。",
      "gapBefore": 0.5,
      "audioDuration": 5.232,
      "audioStart": 419.235,
      "spokenStart": 419.418,
      "spokenEnd": 423.693,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.5
    },
    {
      "id": "c04-p09-u02",
      "sceneId": "c04-p09",
      "chapterIndex": 3,
      "paragraphIndex": 8,
      "utteranceIndex": 1,
      "text": "第三步为每个高风险判断写证据标准：接受哪种一手来源，允许多旧，是否需要独立交叉核验。",
      "gapBefore": 0.25,
      "audioDuration": 9.12,
      "audioStart": 423.762,
      "spokenStart": 423.943,
      "spokenEnd": 432.11,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.25
    },
    {
      "id": "c04-p10-u01",
      "sceneId": "c04-p10",
      "chapterIndex": 3,
      "paragraphIndex": 9,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "第四步才是真实核验：打开来源，对齐具体判断，检查范围和例外，并记录结果。",
      "gapBefore": 0.5,
      "audioDuration": 7.8,
      "audioStart": 432.427,
      "spokenStart": 432.61,
      "spokenEnd": 439.44,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.5
    },
    {
      "id": "c04-p10-u02",
      "sceneId": "c04-p10",
      "chapterIndex": 3,
      "paragraphIndex": 9,
      "utteranceIndex": 1,
      "text": "引用只有真的支持当前依赖的那句话，才算有效证据。",
      "gapBefore": 0.25,
      "audioDuration": 5.064,
      "audioStart": 439.507,
      "spokenStart": 439.69,
      "spokenEnd": 443.782,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.25
    },
    {
      "id": "c04-p11-u01",
      "sceneId": "c04-p11",
      "chapterIndex": 3,
      "paragraphIndex": 10,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "第五步根据证据决定自动继续、澄清、人工批准或停止。",
      "gapBefore": 0.5,
      "audioDuration": 6.024,
      "audioStart": 444.095,
      "spokenStart": 444.282,
      "spokenEnd": 449.334,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.5
    },
    {
      "id": "c04-p11-u02",
      "sceneId": "c04-p11",
      "chapterIndex": 3,
      "paragraphIndex": 10,
      "utteranceIndex": 1,
      "text": "第六步把失败判断、缺失工具和错误评分保存成测试。",
      "gapBefore": 0.25,
      "audioDuration": 5.784,
      "audioStart": 449.399,
      "spokenStart": 449.584,
      "spokenEnd": 454.39,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.25
    },
    {
      "id": "c04-p11-u03",
      "sceneId": "c04-p11",
      "chapterIndex": 3,
      "paragraphIndex": 10,
      "utteranceIndex": 2,
      "text": "订单四八二最终查到周六送达，于是回复被改写，自动退款停在审批门前，这次失败也变成了新的回归测试。",
      "gapBefore": 0.25,
      "audioDuration": 10.2,
      "audioStart": 454.454,
      "spokenStart": 454.64,
      "spokenEnd": 463.873,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.25
    },
    {
      "id": "c04-p11-u04",
      "sceneId": "c04-p11",
      "chapterIndex": 3,
      "paragraphIndex": 10,
      "utteranceIndex": 3,
      "text": "客户最后收到的是当前状态、证据时间和下一次更新条件，而不是未经证明的承诺。",
      "gapBefore": 0.25,
      "audioDuration": 7.848,
      "audioStart": 463.93,
      "spokenStart": 464.123,
      "spokenEnd": 470.98,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.25
    },
    {
      "id": "c04-p12-u01",
      "sceneId": "c04-p12",
      "chapterIndex": 3,
      "paragraphIndex": 11,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "本章小节：先按后果设证据门槛，再用一手和独立证据核验，最后把结果接到行动边界；",
      "gapBefore": 0.5,
      "audioDuration": 8.376,
      "audioStart": 471.292,
      "spokenStart": 471.48,
      "spokenEnd": 478.872,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.5
    },
    {
      "id": "c04-p12-u02",
      "sceneId": "c04-p12",
      "chapterIndex": 3,
      "paragraphIndex": 11,
      "utteranceIndex": 1,
      "text": "清单的价值，不是写一份更长答案，而是阻止未经证明的判断直接改变现实。",
      "gapBefore": 0.25,
      "audioDuration": 7.176,
      "audioStart": 478.947,
      "spokenStart": 479.122,
      "spokenEnd": 485.346,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.25
    },
    {
      "id": "c05-p01-u01",
      "sceneId": "c05-p01",
      "chapterIndex": 4,
      "paragraphIndex": 0,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "AI 智能体猜错，不只是一个神秘故障。",
      "gapBefore": 0.8,
      "audioDuration": 3.96,
      "audioStart": 485.962,
      "spokenStart": 486.146,
      "spokenEnd": 489.144,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.8
    },
    {
      "id": "c05-p01-u02",
      "sceneId": "c05-p01",
      "chapterIndex": 4,
      "paragraphIndex": 0,
      "utteranceIndex": 1,
      "text": "更常见的链条是：信息不足，系统仍奖励回答，然后一条流畅推断未经核验就进入行动。",
      "gapBefore": 0.25,
      "audioDuration": 8.424,
      "audioStart": 489.208,
      "spokenStart": 489.394,
      "spokenEnd": 496.869,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.25
    },
    {
      "id": "c05-p02-u01",
      "sceneId": "c05-p02",
      "chapterIndex": 4,
      "paragraphIndex": 1,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "第一，先问“现在能知道吗”。",
      "gapBefore": 0.5,
      "audioDuration": 2.904,
      "audioStart": 497.183,
      "spokenStart": 497.369,
      "spokenEnd": 499.29,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.5
    },
    {
      "id": "c05-p02-u02",
      "sceneId": "c05-p02",
      "chapterIndex": 4,
      "paragraphIndex": 1,
      "utteranceIndex": 1,
      "text": "检查问题、数据、时效和验证条件，不可答就澄清或明确未知。",
      "gapBefore": 0.25,
      "audioDuration": 6.912,
      "audioStart": 499.365,
      "spokenStart": 499.54,
      "spokenEnd": 505.492,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.25
    },
    {
      "id": "c05-p03-u01",
      "sceneId": "c05-p03",
      "chapterIndex": 4,
      "paragraphIndex": 2,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "第二，把“已经确认”“有支持但不完整”“推断”和“未知”分开写，别让顺滑语气替代证据。",
      "gapBefore": 0.5,
      "audioDuration": 7.368,
      "audioStart": 505.812,
      "spokenStart": 505.992,
      "spokenEnd": 512.391,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.5
    },
    {
      "id": "c05-p04-u01",
      "sceneId": "c05-p04",
      "chapterIndex": 4,
      "paragraphIndex": 3,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "第三，高风险判断必须连接一手证据、必要的独立核验和人工批准。",
      "gapBefore": 0.5,
      "audioDuration": 6.696,
      "audioStart": 512.707,
      "spokenStart": 512.891,
      "spokenEnd": 518.618,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.5
    },
    {
      "id": "c05-p04-u02",
      "sceneId": "c05-p04",
      "chapterIndex": 4,
      "paragraphIndex": 3,
      "utteranceIndex": 1,
      "text": "证据不足时，停止本身就是正确动作。",
      "gapBefore": 0.25,
      "audioDuration": 4.296,
      "audioStart": 518.674,
      "spokenStart": 518.868,
      "spokenEnd": 522.184,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.25
    },
    {
      "id": "c05-p05-u01",
      "sceneId": "c05-p05",
      "chapterIndex": 4,
      "paragraphIndex": 4,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "把这六步 AI 智能体事实核验清单放进工作流：可答性、判断清单、证据标准、真实核验、行动风险、反馈测试。",
      "gapBefore": 0.5,
      "audioDuration": 10.944,
      "audioStart": 522.491,
      "spokenStart": 522.684,
      "spokenEnd": 532.651,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.5
    },
    {
      "id": "c05-p05-u02",
      "sceneId": "c05-p05",
      "chapterIndex": 4,
      "paragraphIndex": 4,
      "utteranceIndex": 1,
      "text": "目标不是让智能体变得胆小，而是让每份自信先获得行动资格。",
      "gapBefore": 0.25,
      "audioDuration": 6.048,
      "audioStart": 532.711,
      "spokenStart": 532.901,
      "spokenEnd": 537.972,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.25
    },
    {
      "id": "c05-p06-u01",
      "sceneId": "c05-p06",
      "chapterIndex": 4,
      "paragraphIndex": 5,
      "utteranceIndex": 0,
      "text": "关注 Tiny Agent，成为更擅长使用 AI 的人！",
      "gapBefore": 0.5,
      "audioDuration": 4.056,
      "audioStart": 538.279,
      "spokenStart": 538.472,
      "spokenEnd": 541.538,
      "actualGapBefore": 0.5
